description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 Minute Body Weight Workout' from the channel WebMD.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Boost your energy and build lean muscle with this full-body fitness routine. It only takes 10 minutes and is perfect for early mornings!
